<lyrics>[V1]
 Hawikom tha bik kaa ngeih cang, Ka herhmi a ka pek dih, A sung bik ka
 Khamhtu bawi, Zumhnak mit in ka zoh i, Zeitik caan paoh ah ka hmuh, Lam
 thluangthluan a ka umpi.

[C1]
   Hal-le-lu-jah Ka Khamhtu he kan kal ti tawn, Ka dawt Khamhtu, Misung
   Khamhtu, A tlingmi a dawtnak chungah a ka chiah i, Keimah lawng a ka
   kaltak bal lo.

[V2]
 Ka sualnak vialte a tawl, Thianghlim tein a ka chiah A sung bik ka
 Khamhtu bawi, Ngandamnak a ka pek i, Hnangamnak bia a ka ruah, Nifa
 thluachuah a ka pek.

[C2]
   Hal-le-lu-jah Ka Khamhtu he kan kal ti tawn, Ka dawt Khamhtu, Misung
   Khamhtu, A tlingmi a dawtnak chungah a ka chiah i, Keimah lawng a ka
   kaltak bal lo.

[V3]
 Vansannak ka ton zongah, Mirh zimziam in a ka hnemh, A sung bik ka
 Khamhtu bawi, Ka phut lomi dinnak cu, A tang ah pom in ka hmuh, Bawmtu ka
 Bawipa a si.

[C3]
   Hal-le-lu-jah Ka Khamhtu he kan kal ti tawn, Ka dawt Khamhtu, Misung
   Khamhtu, A tlingmi a dawtnak chungah a ka chiah i, Keimah lawng a ka
   kaltak bal lo.

[V4]
 Umnak inn a kan timhpiak, Lungvar tamhmi tikam ah, A sung bik ka
 Khamhtu Bawi, Nunnak ni bang a liam cun, Khi varal ah ka um lai, Zungzal
 ceunak khuapi ah,

[C4]
   Hal-le-lu-jah Ka Khamhtu he kan kal ti tawn, Ka dawt Khamhtu, Misung
   Khamhtu, A tlingmi a dawtnak chungah a ka chiah i, Keimah lawng a ka
   kaltak bal lo.</lyrics>
<title>HAWIKOM THA BIK KAA NGEIH CANG CH178</title>
<hymn_number>178</hymn_number>
</song>